1. Adding a Meal:
Click "Add Meal" in the navigation
Enter the meal name - nutrition data will be automatically fetched as you type
Fill in other details and save

2. Viewing Meals:
The homepage shows all your meals
Use the search box to find specific meals
Filter by category using the dropdown

3. Generating Reports:
Click "Nutrition Report" in the navigation
View totals, averages, and category breakdowns
See your highest calorie meals
